        "content": "<p>Hello all! This is the thread of discussion for the talk of Gioele Zardini, David I. Spivak, Andrea Censi and Emilio Frazzoli, \"A Compositional Sheaf-Theoretic Framework for Event-Based Systems\".<br>\nDate and time: Tuesday July 7, 17:10 UTC.<br>\nZoom meeting: <a href=\"https://mit.zoom.us/j/7055345747\">https://mit.zoom.us/j/7055345747</a><br>\nYouTube live stream: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Is5mWZcCVf0&amp;list=PLCOXjXDLt3pZDHGYOIqtg1m1lLOURjl1Q\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Is5mWZcCVf0&amp;list=PLCOXjXDLt3pZDHGYOIqtg1m1lLOURjl1Q</a></p>\n<div class=\"youtube-video message_inline_image\"><a data-id=\"Is5mWZcCVf0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Is5mWZcCVf0&amp;list=PLCOXjXDLt3pZDHGYOIqtg1m1lLOURjl1Q\"><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Is5mWZcCVf0/default.jpg\"></a></div>",
